# Rules

## Cursor Rules Location
Cursor Rules must be placed in .cursor/rules/ directory with .mdc extension.

# Examples

## Valid
```
.cursor/rules/my-rule.mdc
.cursor/rules/another-rule.mdc
```

## Invalid
```
rules/my-rule.mdc
.cursor/my-rule.mdc
.cursor/rules/my-rule.txt
```